    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
