    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist's specification, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine with its distinct independent throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its precision with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a carbon fiber roof to minimize the polar moment of inertia. Mechanically sound, the vehicle has undergone critical preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. It presents in honest condition with minor road-derived patina, offering a mechanically robust platform for the discerning driver who values atmospheric induction and hydraulic steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. All service records available. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
