    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with daily reliability. The exterior retains its original factory shine, though a discerning eye will notice minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014purely cosmetic and consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather upholstery remains soft and free of cracks, while all electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control and premium audio system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the brake pads and rotors have significant life left. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. It currently sits on a set of all-season tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner who appreciates a car that has been respected and properly looked after.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
