      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in wonderful shape, super clean inside and out, and has plenty of life left in it. It's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure. Perfect for road trips or just zipping around town\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
